Package automation.utils

Class Constants

  • java.lang.Object
    • automation.utils.Constants
  • public class Constants
extends Object
    The Constants class stores commonly used constants such as URLs, user credentials, and API keys for the application.

    This class is designed to centralize constants used throughout the automation framework, making it easier to maintain and update values in a single place.
